Set this environment variable to automatically connect to the backend.
```
export FIRESTORE_EMULATOR_HOST="localhost:8080"
```

To index the dataset on Algolia, which should only be done when making permanent changes to the test data or for testing Algolia, labspoon/functions/.runtimeconfig.json must have the following values set, which can be retrieved from the Algolia dashboard:

```
{
  "algolia": {
    "admin_key": "",
    "app_id": "",
    "search_key": ""
  }
}
```
